lead_paragraph: New York Yankees right-hander Luis Severino was ejected after hitting Toronto's Justin Smoak with a pitch in the second inning Monday night, leading to an angry shoving match between the teams.

headline.print_headline: Yankees, Blue Jays Scrap After 3 HBP in First 2 Innings
